# Global sapling ignore — applies to all sapling repos on this machine
# that don't already cover these patterns in their own .gitignore/.slignore.
#
# Mirror of ~/.config/git/ignore because sapling does NOT read git's global
# excludesfile. Keep them in sync when adding new entries.
#
# Wired into sapling via [ui] ignore = ~/.config/sapling/ignore in sapling.conf.

